title: Pictures: Joe Kittinger honored with naming of Casselberry Post Office - Orlando Sentinel
text:
Scenes from the dedication ceremony naming the Casselberry Post Office after Joe Kittinger, Tuesday, April 15, 2025. Kittinger, who passed away in 2022, was a decorated veteran, former prisoner of war and a legendary Central Floridian known for his pioneering achievements in aviation and space history. (Joe Burbank/Orlando Sentinel)
The Lake Howell High School Navy Junior ROTC honor guard presents the colors during the dedication ceremony at the Casselberry Post Office honoring Colonel Joe Kittinger, Tuesday, April 15, 2025. Kittinger, who passed away in 2022, was a decorated veteran, former prisoner of war and a legendary Central Floridian known for his pioneering achievements in aviation and space history.
